Package: surveySHAP
Type: Package
Title: SHAP-Based Interpretation Tools for Survey Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jingtian", "Yu",
           email = "your_email@domain.edu",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    Tools for interpreting machine learning models applied to survey data,
    with a focus on ordinal and continuous policy preference outcomes.
    The package provides SHAP-based utilities, visualization helpers,
    and a curated processed survey dataset for reproducible examples.
